## Purpose


The purpose of this document is to establish a clear, actionable plan for the optimization of user interface and user experience (UI/UX) flows within our digital platforms. This endeavor will ensure that our members have seamless, intuitive interactions that support their healing journeys through our PMA's unique offerings.


